headline: Zentra Completes Integration with Schlage® XE360™ Series
summary: Allegion US, a leading provider of security solutions, technology and services, will showcase the seamless integration of Schlage XE360™ electronic locks with Zentra, a game-changing access control solution for property managers and facility executives, at Apartmentalize.
